<br>
I so hate it so much, when your girlfriend for so many months/years, just suddenly wakes up one day and have lost all the love, that were the building blocks of the relationsship.<br>
I miss her so much, and the worst thing is...<br>
That I would give her everything, I would do everything.<br>
God it sucks when you stand there willing to give everything, and all that you are...Only to have the other person to say...&quot;No, I am not in love with you any more...&quot;<br>
It hurts so much.<br>
<br>
Not that EQ is any of the reasons why she left, but somehow I still think that EQ is one of the things.<br>
And I can tell all of you, that EQ is just not worth it, if you do not pay enough attention to your girlfriend. You will only regret it so much...<br>
I cannot recommend it to anyone else, to go through what I have gone through today.<br>
<br>
I miss her so...And I regret the time I have spend in EQ, that I should have spend on her.<br>
<br>
(And yes, I have been out drinking the pain away, even though that is the worst that you can do.) <br>
 <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">General <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Stoppelton Starkweather</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=695966" target="top">Magelo profile</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=maushi>Maushi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 114<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/5/03 12:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1722.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: I did it as well....(Might fit better in here)</span><hr size=1> Why would you want to be with someone that doesnt want to be with you ? Grow some pride bud.<br>
