<br>
I will pleed, cry and kneel down for forgiveness when I fuck up but when someone decides to stop sending love my way I just walk away.  <br>
<br>
Does it hurt ? It sure does.  Will it last forever ? Of course not.<br>
<br>
Even if you disagree pride sometimes allows you to be realistic.<br>
<br>
